text: Sukhoi Su-30 is a Russian fighter aircraft. It is developed by Sukhoi Aviation Corporation. It is a 4.5-generation jet fighter aircraft. The aircraft is used by these air forces: *Algerian Air Force *Angolan Air Force *People's Liberation Army Air Force *Indian Air Force *Indonesian Air Force *Kazakh Air Force *Royal Malaysian Air Force *Russian Air Force *Uganda Air Force *Venezuelan Air Force *Vietnam People's Air Force == Versions == Su-30K Export version of the basic Su-30 Su-30MKI Version for India Su-30SM Version of the Su-30MKI for Russia Category:Russian military aircraft Category:Sukhoi aircraft
title: Sukhoi Su-30
